{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a89c87a9dd","title":"希望各军区党委报告第一期整风情况","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a12700ad3b","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":16,"articleId":"a89c87a9dd"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"85f9bc2d7d","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a89c87a9dd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会总政治部起草的给各大军区党委并告各中央局的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4ca8ab513e","type":"title","text":"希望各军区党委报告第一期整风情况”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a89c87a9dd"},{"id":"85f9bc2d7d","type":"paragraph","text":"各大军区党委，并告各中央局","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a89c87a9dd"},{"id":"47e0644043","type":"paragraph","text":"地方党的整风工作，业已普遍进行，并向中央发来了许多报告，提出了许多好的经验；但军队党的整风工作是否已在进行及如何进行的，除少数有反映外，大多数尚无反映。我们希望各军区党委务于九月底或十月初向我们发来一次报告，概述全区部队第一期整风情况，如何，盼复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a89c87a9dd"},{"id":"7d26b2817c","type":"paragraph","text":"军委总政","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a89c87a9dd"},{"id":"900da7ba15","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a89c87a9dd"}],"page":{"id":"170f65487c","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"a89c87a9dd","start":160,"end":160}}}},"__N_SSG":true}